Summary: Like a 7-8 story building on its side.
divs: Sighting DetailsAt about 4am. The wind started blowing very hard. I woke-up and coming over a cliff I saw what looked like a building going over head slowly. It was low enough I could see shapes and objects on it. My brother myself and a friend (he is a deputy sheriff now) saw 5-6 objects in the sky making zig-zag patterns in the sky in fractions of a second. On a clear night full moon. Around 10pm.
trends: There have been no other sightings in Watonga
